snippet.title: FUUJIN RYOUIKI: ERETZVAJU (PS1) - Intro / Opening (Evil Zone Japanese Version)
snippet.description:
Fuujin Ryouiki: Eretzvaju intro / opening. 
Its duration is shorter than the American version, and has the song Kiss In The Dark.

Evil Zone Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL-qTFulmnf4rbsX8TY0zV7D

Release data:
Evil Zone / Fuujin Ryouiki: Eretzvaju (1999)
Genre: Fighting
Platform: Playstation (PSX / PS1 / PS)
Developer: Yuke's
Publisher: Yuke's / Titus Software

Recorded with Live Gamer Portable 2 - GC510.
